{
  "texts": [
    "The emphasis on environmentally sound cybersecurity within the renewable energy sector highlights a move toward security measures that both protect and sustain energy infrastructure.",
    "This is essential for the long-term viability of renewable energy systems, where technological security and environmental sustainability intersect.",
    "The congressional research report by [48] focuses on transitioning toward energy solutions driven by the imperative of green cybersecurity for the use and maintenance of physical infrastructure.",
    "Modernizing the grid is inherently tied to enhancing its efficiency and reducing its environmental impact, aligning with SDG 7.3 and SDG 13.2.",
    "The Space 4.0 framework [49] parallels these concerns."
  ]
}